We're just trying to
do our best to keep

00:45:38.190 --> 00:45:40.990
our money in the great
state of Michigan,

00:45:40.990 --> 00:45:43.620
especially in the
city, and start to--

00:45:43.620 --> 00:45:45.900
you can see the change.

00:45:45.900 --> 00:45:48.000
You can visibly
reach out and see

00:45:48.000 --> 00:45:52.599
how your money that you spend
on tomatoes is making an impact.

00:45:52.599 --> 00:45:53.585
It's powerful stuff.

